ve但係之前睇過啲news話eve嗰陣有問題？就冇再食過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"上面篇文話有加唔少少鎮定劑<br />\n<br />\n第一個大家比較熟悉，就是咖啡因，會加強止痛藥的效果，普拿疼加強錠也是添加這個；第二個，Allylisopropylacetylurea是甚麼東西呢？<br />\n它其實是一種鎮定劑，效果不是非常強，有點解除焦慮的作用，某種程度上可能可以幫助止痛藥的效果，1926年就發明出來了；其他國家目前沒有繼續用的原因，是因為後來有些人出現了血小板低下、全身性紫斑出血的副作用，所以就停用了。不過日本繼續用了這麼多年，看起來好像也還好就是了。"},{"pid":"a0f316caa5ba005b62b5b5c427742d5c4549b206","tid":2393622,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145e76263d513790b97b8b5e12301d0c5d4ff4cb","tid":2393622,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f3a9fc2f2180f9810a4a1f3f2ce0ef9fa783f1","tid":2393622,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"有用資訊！"},{"pid":"938bb9e9fff270ad5846e30beb55b3a07898b829","tid":2393622,"uid":159258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"donki有賣eve咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4965de139d5779e5be028276e7556d759c31cbd4","tid":2393622,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"eve係幾有效<br />\n但唔建議食太多"},{"pid":"45e434a33eddacccc48aea95527d82119148536b","tid":2393622,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4965de139d5779e5be028276e7556d759c31cbd4","tid":2393622,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"eve係幾有效<br />\n但唔建議食太多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"點解？"},{"pid":"ece623ef551809a8e128a65253df22a25d823901","tid":2393622,"uid":278814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"咁請問樓主：GSK同Sanofi合作研發嘅疫苗，將來研發成功都會抵制埋？<img src=\"/ass